org.sakaiproject.tool.assessment.ui.bean.author

Class CalculatedQuestionFormulaBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sakaiproject.tool.assessment.ui.bean.author.CalculatedQuestionFormulaBean
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, CalculatedQuestionAnswerIfc

    public class CalculatedQuestionFormulaBean
extends Object
implements Serializable, CalculatedQuestionAnswerIfc
    CalculatedQuestionFormulaBean contains the formula for the answer for a Calculated question. The formula contains references to CalculatedQuestionVariableBeans, which allows a test to have different variables and answers each time that it is taken.
    Author:
    mgillian
